barrel_id = 11
barrel_name = "Pit Boss"
barrel_desc = "[b]Pit Boss Barrel[/b]
Barrel collected from the Pit Boss. Grant you ability similar to its owner.

Possible rolls:
[ul]
Empowered Dash: Gain bonus dash speed for a short amount of time after you shoot a bullet.
Fortitude: Recover a small amount of health over time.
Death From Above: Increased damage when midair and increased crit chance when shoot downward.
Tag n Shred: Reduced initial damage, but increased damage for every projectile hit target.
[/ul]"
